    <item>
      <title>贸易战期间中国通过每日汇率维持人民币支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/china-maintains-yuan-support-via-daily-fixing-amid-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中美贸易紧张局势不断升级，加大了人民币贬值压力，中国将人民币每日参考汇率设定在7.2以上的水平，加大了对人民币的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/china-maintains-yuan-support-via-daily-fixing-amid-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:22:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度新任储备银行行长改变了交易员的策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/new-reserve-bank-of-india-governor-shakes-up-traders-playbook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙克提坎塔·达斯担任印度央行行长最后两年，卢比汇率坚挺，流动性减少，利率居高不下。桑杰·马洛特拉似乎将打破这一模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/new-reserve-bank-of-india-governor-shakes-up-traders-playbook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 01:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美贸易战刺激避险需求，黄金创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-trade-war-stokes-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中美贸易战的爆发刺激了避险需求，金价在上一交易日上涨近 1% 后，升至历史新高。]]></description>
